- How much time do you want me to do?
- What would you like to do?

01:19:46.325 --> 01:19:49.283
- Zero.
- Okay. Perfect.

01:19:49.367 --> 01:19:52.283
- How much are you gonna do, Tig?
- Probably 45.

01:19:52.367 --> 01:19:53.325
- Oh, you are?
- Yeah.

01:19:53.408 --> 01:19:54.992
Oh, okay.

01:19:55.075 --> 01:19:56.450
Uh, what?

01:19:56.533 --> 01:19:57.742
- I know.
- You're gonna host?

01:20:03.533 --> 01:20:05.783
Flowers from my brother.

01:20:05.867 --> 01:20:09.075
It says, "To my beautiful
and amazing sister,

01:20:09.158 --> 01:20:11.742
I love you and am so proud of you.

01:20:11.825 --> 01:20:15.283
The only person that would be more proud
would be our mother.

01:20:15.367 --> 01:20:17.700
Good luck tonight.
Love, your brother, Renaud."

01:20:28.867 --> 01:20:31.617
Well, this is what
I'll be saying tonight.

01:20:34.658 --> 01:20:36.658
What if this show is a bomb?

01:20:36.742 --> 01:20:39.200
Oh, my God,
it's not gonna happen.

01:20:39.283 --> 01:20:42.158
Tonight's the most nervous I've seen her,
you know, before this show.

01:20:42.242 --> 01:20:43.450
Because this is the show back.

01:20:43.533 --> 01:20:46.450
I grew up in the streets
of the Grove and...

01:20:48.533 --> 01:20:50.700
Tig is usually
a very cool customer.

01:20:50.783 --> 01:20:54.492
You never really see her frazzled.

01:20:54.575 --> 01:20:57.158
But that night,
she may have been nervous.

01:20:57.242 --> 01:21:01.200
...say things like,
"Not on my watch" and stuff.

01:21:01.283 --> 01:21:02.742
All right.

01:21:02.825 --> 01:21:05.783
Let's get to the reason
why we're all here.

01:21:05.867 --> 01:21:07.450
Oh, boy.

01:21:07.533 --> 01:21:10.700
God, I remember the day
she was born. The, um...

01:21:12.867 --> 01:21:16.950
The doctor put her on my belly
and she was covered in all this goop,

01:21:17.033 --> 01:21:19.325
and I just said,

01:21:19.408 --> 01:21:20.450
"Tig.

01:21:21.908 --> 01:21:24.450
I'll call her Tig."

01:21:24.533 --> 01:21:30.075
Please welcome
my friend, Tig Notaro.

01:21:37.617 --> 01:21:39.117
How's it going?

01:21:40.742 --> 01:21:42.283
Thank you.

01:21:42.367 --> 01:21:45.158
I don't have cancer.
Hello, how are you?

01:21:49.533 --> 01:21:54.533
Thank you so much.
You guys have been so, so great.

01:21:55.533 --> 01:21:56.700
Oh, my gosh.

01:21:57.992 --> 01:22:01.200
I was diagnosed
with bilateral breast cancer.

01:22:02.283 --> 01:22:03.867
Word has not gotten out, so...

01:22:06.825 --> 01:22:12.117
And before my diagnosis
and the surgery,

01:22:12.200 --> 01:22:16.033
I was pretty...
just relatively flat-chested.

01:22:16.950 --> 01:22:20.117
And I've made
so many jokes over the years

01:22:20.200 --> 01:22:23.783
about how flat-chested I was.

01:22:23.867 --> 01:22:26.575
I started to think that maybe...

01:22:26.658 --> 01:22:30.033
my boobs overheard me...

01:22:37.992 --> 01:22:41.033
and were just, like,
"You know what?

01:22:44.908 --> 01:22:46.867
We are sick of this.

01:22:50.367 --> 01:22:51.908
Let's kill her."

01:22:56.200 --> 01:23:00.617
I couldn't believe that I was back onstage
doing an hour of material.

01:23:00.700 --> 01:23:04.533
I felt like the intro to Mary Tyler Moore.

01:23:04.617 --> 01:23:10.283
I felt like I tossed my hat in the air,
and I just felt like I was back.

01:23:10.367 --> 01:23:11.992
Good night.

01:23:19.533 --> 01:23:22.742
Ready to adopt children?

01:23:22.825 --> 01:23:24.950
Can't wait.

01:23:25.033 --> 01:23:27.283
You don't have to.

01:23:27.367 --> 01:23:28.450
- Hi.
- Hi.

01:23:31.367 --> 01:23:35.408
We've both, sort of, decided
that we wanna look into adoption,

01:23:35.492 --> 01:23:38.908
and I'm also interested
in having kids of my own together.

01:23:39.033 --> 01:23:40.408
So I think we're gonna end up

01:23:40.492 --> 01:23:43.408
having a bunch of kids
in different ways.

01:23:47.533 --> 01:23:50.325
We need to get a subscription
to Parent magazine...

01:23:50.408 --> 01:23:52.117
immediately.

01:23:52.200 --> 01:23:53.950
Hello.

01:23:54.033 --> 01:23:56.033
- Hi.
- How are you guys? I'm Jennifer.

01:23:56.117 --> 01:23:57.617
- Oh, I'm Tig.
- Tig, nice to meet you.

01:23:57.700 --> 01:23:59.460
- Hi, Stephanie.
- Stephanie, nice to meet you.

01:23:59.492 --> 01:24:00.867
Come on back.

01:24:05.033 --> 01:24:08.408
Are we gonna put all our bathroom stuff
together in the one downstairs?

01:24:08.492 --> 01:24:10.408
I have no idea.

01:24:10.492 --> 01:24:13.700
It'll all be a mystery
that unfolds.

01:24:19.242 --> 01:24:22.117
Buying this house
has been bittersweet

01:24:22.200 --> 01:24:25.575
because it's the greatest place.

01:24:25.658 --> 01:24:27.200
I wish my mother could be here

01:24:27.283 --> 01:24:31.367
to see what Stephanie and I
are building together,

01:24:31.450 --> 01:24:34.367
and I wish that I could...

01:24:36.242 --> 01:24:38.742
share Stephanie with my mother.

01:24:40.533 --> 01:24:42.117
In here.

01:24:42.200 --> 01:24:44.242
This is where children are gonna go.

01:24:44.325 --> 01:24:46.825
We're gonna have
two single beds.

01:24:46.908 --> 01:24:50.492
We'll put one little
newborn infant on each bed

01:24:50.575 --> 01:24:52.742
and just hope
they stay there at night.

01:24:52.825 --> 01:24:54.325
We'll just tell them to stay.

01:24:54.408 --> 01:24:56.992
Oh, yeah, we'll just tell them
to stay in bed.

01:24:57.075 --> 01:24:58.617
This definitely feels like...

01:24:59.617 --> 01:25:02.075
- the beginning of the family.
- Yeah.

01:25:09.283 --> 01:25:12.117
Going through everything that I did,

01:25:12.200 --> 01:25:16.867
it has changed my life as a person,
as a performer.

01:25:16.950 --> 01:25:19.533
I just feel so much more keenly aware

01:25:19.617 --> 01:25:23.908
of how happy and thankful I am
for what I have,

01:25:23.992 --> 01:25:26.450
and I... I feel very lucky.

01:25:28.950 --> 01:25:33.825
This is what being alive is all about.

01:25:33.908 --> 01:25:38.867
Just that idea of taking risks
and seeing the payoff.

01:25:38.950 --> 01:25:42.783
You know, it's so cliché,
but it's like you're alive...

01:25:44.533 --> 01:25:47.617
so you might as well take chances.

01:25:47.700 --> 01:25:49.742
This is so exciting.

